General.Name: Stayble Therapeutics AB
General.Description: Stayble Therapeutics AB (publ) develops injectable treatment for chronic low back pain triggered by disc degeneration. The company develops STA363, a minimally invasive single injection of the drug into the disc that targets chronic low back pain. Stayble Therapeutics AB (publ) was incorporated in 2015 and is based in Gothenburg, Sweden.
